        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/27490850/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/27490850/" class="">第20页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/Aubrey2010/" class=" " title="半半">半半</a>
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="27490850">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">猪是否能快乐的像人，我们不知道；但是人会容易满足得像猪，我们时常看见的。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2013-07-08 20:43</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                猪是否能快乐的像人，我们不知道；但是人会容易满足得像猪，我们时常看见的。
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

<a href="https://www.douban.com/accounts/register?reason=collect" class="j a_show_login lnk-sharing lnk-douban-sharing">推荐</a>
